.TH MPI_Win_Lock 3 "6/24/2006" "LAM/MPI 7.1.4" "LAM/MPI"
.SH NAME
MPI_Win_Lock \-  Starts an RMA access epoch 
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
#include <mpi.h>
int MPI_Win_lock(int lock_type, int rank, int assert, MPI_Win win)
.fi
.SH INPUT PARAMETERS
.PD 0
.TP
.B lock_type 
- either MPI_LOCK_EXCLUSIVE or MPI_LOCK_SHARED (state)
.PD 1
.PD 0
.TP
.B rank 
- rank of locked window (nonnegative integer)
.PD 1
.PD 0
.TP
.B assert 
- program assertion (integer)
.PD 1
.PD 0
.TP
.B win 
- window object (handle)
.PD 1

.SH NOTES

This function is currently not implemented in LAM/MPI.  It will return
an MPI_ERR_OTHER run time error.

